%20a%20Powerball%20lottery%20ticket%20on%20January%206%2C%202023%2C%20which%20has%20become%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20heated%20dispute%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F18%2Fman-sues-powerball-lottery-win-error%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20missing%20the%20Powerball%20drawing%20the%20next%20day%2C%20Mr%20Cheeks%20was%20astonished%20to%20find%20his%20numbers%20listed%20on%20the%20DC%20Lottery's%20website%20just%20two%20days%20later%2C%20the%20report%20added.%20Powerball%20and%20the%20DC%20Lottery%2C%20however%2C%20contend%20that%20his%20numbers%20were%20published%20in%20error%2C%20sparking%20a%20contentious%20legal%20battle%20over%20the%20rightful%20winner%20of%20the%20massive%20jackpot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcwashington.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fman-sues-after-340m-powerball-prize-denied-due-to-dc-lottery-website-mistake%2F3545547%2F%5C%22%3ENBC%20Washington%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Cheeks%20recalled%20his%20initial%20reaction%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20a%20little%20excited%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20shout%2C%20I%20didn't%20scream.%20I%20just%20politely%20called%20a%20friend.%20I%20took%20a%20picture%20as%20he%20recommended%2C%20and%20that%20was%20it.%20I%20went%20to%20sleep.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20upon%20submitting%20his%20ticket%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20Lottery%20and%20Gaming%20(OLG)%2C%20Cheeks%20faced%20rejection%20of%20his%20claim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20court%20documents%20stated%20that%20the%20administrators%20denied%20Mr%20Cheeks'%20jackpot%20claim.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20him%2C%20they%20explained%20that%20his%20prize%20claim%20was%20denied%20because%20the%20ticket%20was%20not%20validated%20as%20a%20winner%20by%20the%20OLG's%20gaming%20system%2C%20as%20required%20by%20OLG%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20claims%20agents%20told%20me%20my%20ticket%20was%20no%20good%2C%20just%20to%20throw%20it%20in%20the%20trash%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Cheeks%20recounted%20to%20the%20BBC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20remembered%20responding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20gave%20him%20a%20stern%20look.%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98In%20the%20trash%20can%3F'%20%E2%80%98Oh%20yeah%2C%20just%20throw%20it%20away.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20paid.%20There's%20a%20trash%20can%20right%20there.'%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cheeks%20chose%20not%20to%20discard%20his%20ticket%20but%20instead%20placed%20it%20in%20a%20safe%20deposit%20box%20and%20sought%20legal%20counsel%20to%20file%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Powerball.%20The%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20Mr%20Cheeks%20also%20names%20the%20Multi-State%20Lottery%20Association%20and%20game%20contractor%20Taoti%20Enterprises%20as%20defendants%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20currently%20seeking%20damages%20from%20the%20lottery%2C%20amounting%20to%20the%20Powerball%20jackpot%2C%20plus%20the%20daily%20interest%20he%20would%20have%20earned%20on%20it%2C%20totalling%20%24340%20million%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cheeks%20is%20now%20suing%20for%20eight%20separate%20counts%2C%20including%20breach%20of%20contract%2C%20negligence%2C%20infliction%20of%20emotional%20distress%2C%20and%20fraud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20lawyer%2C%20Richard%20Evans%2C%20argues%20that%20because%20the%20winning%20numbers%20matched%20Mr%20Cheeks'%20numbers%2C%20he%20should%20receive%20the%20entire%20jackpot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20lawsuit%20raises%20critical%20questions%20about%20the%20integrity%20and%20accountability%20of%20lottery%20operations%20and%20the%20safeguards%20-%20or%20lack%20thereof%20-%20against%20the%20type%20of%20errors%20that%20Powerball%20and%20the%20DC%20Lottery%20contend%20occurred%20in%20this%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Evans%20stated%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ev