Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107840842.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20source%20further%20said%20that%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Aditya%20Chopra%20and%20his%20team%20have%20diligently%20crafted%20the%20script%20for%20Pathaan%202%2C%20envisioning%20it%20as%20the%20flagship%20spy%20film%20within%20the%20universe%2C%20poised%20to%20establish%20the%20groundwork%20for%20a%20larger%20conflict%20in%20the%20future%2C%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20the%20impending%20showdown%20between%20Tiger%20and%20Pathaan%20(Tiger%20vs.%20Pathaan)%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20timeline%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-to-reunite-with-aditya-chopra-for-pathaan-2-to-go-on-floors-in-december-reports%2Farticleshow%2F107840842.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Eknath%20Shinde's%20Maratha%20Quota%20Move%20Faces%20High%20Odds%2C%20A%20History%20Of%20Setbacks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20holds%20a%20special%20Assembly%20session%20today%20on%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20issue%2C%20it%20will%20add%20another%20chapter%20to%20the%20long%20history%20of%20the%20community's%20fight%20for%20quota%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20attempts%20by%20state%20governments%20to%20introduce%20reservation%20for%20Marathas%20have%20been%20struck%20down%20by%20courts.%20But%20waves%20of%20protests%20and%20the%20community's%20political%20significance%20have%20led%20to%20repeated%20revivals%20of%20the%20sensitive%20issue.%20The%20community%20accounts%20for%2033%20per%20cent%20of%20Maharashtra's%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20latest%20push%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20has%20said%20reservation%20to%20Marathas%20will%20be%20given%20according%20to%20the%20law%20after%20presenting%20a%20survey%20report%20during%20the%20day-long%20session%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20survey%20has%20been%20conducted%20on%20nearly%202-2.5%20crore%20people.%20On%20February%2020%2C%20we%20have%20called%20a%20special%20session%20of%20the%20assembly%20after%20which%20Maratha%20reservation%20will%20be%20given%20according%20to%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government's%20latest%20move%20on%20the%20quota%20issue%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20protest%20led%20by%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%2C%20who%20has%20started%20an%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%20at%20his%20village%20in%20Jalna%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Maratha%20Arc%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maratha%20community%2C%20which%20gained%20prominence%20with%20Shivaji's%20founding%20of%20the%20Maratha%20empire%20in%20the%2017th%20century%2C%20is%20more%20a%20caste%20cluster%20than%20one%20caste.%20The%20British%20records%20used%20%26quot%3BMaratha%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20term%20to%20denote%20elite%20layers%20within%20various%20castes.%20Post%20Independence%2C%20the%20community%20opposed%20any%20reservation%20because%20they%20did%20not%20want%20the%20%26quot%3Bbackward%26quot%3B%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20income%20from%20agriculture%20declined%2C%20murmurs%20began.%20In%20the%201980s%2C%20caste%20politics%20came%20to%20the%20forefront%20after%20the%20Mandal%20commission%20report.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20Anna%20Saheb%20Patil%2C%20then%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20started%20a%20movement%20in%20demand%20of%20reservation%20for%20Marathas.%20This%20was%2C%20however%2C%20a%20demand%20for%20quota%20based%20on%20economic%20criteria%20and%20not%20caste.%20But%20as%20caste%20politics%20gained%20currency%20following%20the%20VP%20Singh%20government's%20move%20to%20implement%20the%20Mandal%20commission%20report%2C%20leaders%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20agitation%20started%20seeking%20benefits%20under%20the%20OBC%20category.%20This%20was%20opposed%20by%20OBC%20leaders%2C%20who%20say%20their%20share%20in%20government%20jobs%20and%20benefits%20will%20shrink%20if%20Marathas%20are%20added%20to%20the%20quota%20list.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20three%20central%20and%20three%20state%20commissions%20have%20refused%20to%20identity%20the%20Marathas%20as%20backward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Attempts%2C%20The%20Setbacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20just%20before%20the%20election%2C%20the%20then%20Congress%20government%20under%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20implemented%20a%2016%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20Marathas.%20The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20struck%20it%20down%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20already%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20reservation%20cannot%20exceed%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20wave%20of%20a%20quota%20demand%20came%20in%202016-2017%2C%20shortly%20after%20a%2015-year-old%20Maratha%20girl%20was%20gangraped%20and%20murdered%20at%20Kopardi%20village%20in%20Ahmednagar%20district.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20then%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20government%20announced%2016%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20Marathas.%20This%20was%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202021%20on%20two%20grounds%20--%20it%20breached%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20quota%20ceiling%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20'extraordinary%20circumstance'%20to%20justify%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Eknath%20Shinde%20government%20is%20now%20making%20a%20third%20push%20to%20bring%20reservation%20for%20Marathas.%20This%20legislation%20proposes%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20the%20community%20in%20jobs%20and%20education.%20The%20cabinet%20has%20cleared%20the%20proposal%20and%20it%20will%20now%20be%20tabled%20in%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708406400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fgsec9hh8_e