%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ladakh%20Innovator%20Threatens%20%26quot%3BFast%20Unto%20Death%26quot%3B%20Ahead%20Of%20Talks%20With%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESonam%20Wangchuk%2C%20a%20key%20campaigner%20for%20constitutional%20safeguards%20for%20Ladakh%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20the%20proposed%20%26quot%3Bfast%20unto%20death%26quot%3B%20protest%20will%20be%20reviewed%20next%20week%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20Centre%20over%20their%20various%20demands%2C%20including%20statehood%20to%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20call%20a%20very%20big%20public%20gathering%20in%20Leh%20city%20on%20February%2026%20to%20either%20thank%20the%20government%20for%20accepting%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20or%20go%20for%20a%20fast%20unto%20death%20in%20case%20the%20talks%20fail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Wangchuk%2C%20who%20was%20set%20to%20begin%20a%20hunger%20strike%20till%20death%20from%20Tuesday%20in%20support%20of%20the%20demands%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ladakh%20leadership%2C%20which%20is%20presently%20camping%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20temporarily%20dropped%20the%20%26quot%3Bfast%20unto%20death%26quot%3B%20programme%20after%20a%20fresh%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20central%20government%20on%20Monday%2C%20terming%20the%20development%20as%20significant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20Centre%20had%20agreed%20to%20discuss%20threadbare%20the%20demands%20for%20Ladakh's%20statehood%2C%20inclusion%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20in%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20an%20exclusive%20public%20service%20commission%20for%20the%20high-altitude%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20was%20agreed%20during%20a%20meeting%20between%20the%20High%20Powered%20Committee%20(HPC)%20for%20Ladakh%2C%20headed%20by%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Nityanand%20Rai%2C%20and%20a%2014-member%20delegation%20of%20the%20Apex%20Body%20of%20Leh%20(ABL)%20and%20the%20Kargil%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(KDA)%2C%20representing%20various%20organisations%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20also%20resolved%20to%20constitute%20a%20joint%20sub-committee%20for%20carrying%20forward%20the%20exercise%20to%20look%20into%20the%20details%20of%20the%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20wait%20till%20the%20February%2024%20meeting%20of%20the%20sub-committee%20and%20the%20return%20of%20our%20leaders%20to%20Leh%20on%20February%2025.%20We%20will%20call%20a%20very%20big%20public%20gathering%20the%20next%20day%20in%20Leh%20city%20to%20either%20thank%20the%20government%20for%20meeting%20our%20demands%20or%20start%20our%20fast%20unto%20death%20in%20case%20the%20talks%20fail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Wangchuk%2C%20a%20winner%20of%20the%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20delegation%20are%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20--%20one%20for%20Kargil%20and%20one%20for%20Leh%20--%20and%20job%20opportunities%20for%20residents%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory.%20Ladakh%20currently%20has%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELadakh%2C%20which%20no%20longer%20has%20any%20assembly%20constituency%2C%20was%20earlier%20part%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20provisions%20of%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20which%20gave%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20were%20abrogated%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20and%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20was%20bifurcated%20into%20the%20Union%20territories%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20provisions%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20made%20a%20Union%20Territory%20with%20a%20legislative%20assembly%20and%20Ladakh%20a%20Union%20Territory%20without%20an%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20four%20representatives%20from%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Centre%20assured%20the%20delegation%20from%20Ladakh%20in%20December%20that%20it%20was%20committed%20to%20fast-tracking%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20and%20meeting%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assurance%20was%20given%20at%20a%20meeting%20held%20with%20the%20HPC%20for%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20formed%20the%20HPC%20for%20Ladakh%20under%20Mr%20Rai's%20chairmanship%20with%20a%20mandate%20to%20discuss%20the%20measures%20needed%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20protect%20the%20region's%20unique%20culture%20and%20language%2C%20taking%20into%20consideration%20its%20geographical%20location%20and%20strategic%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20HPC%20has%20also%20been%20formed%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20land%20and%20employment%2C%20measures%20for%20inclusive%20development%20and%20employment%20generation%20in%20the%20region%2C%20steps%20related%20to%20the%20empowerment%20of%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Development%20Councils%20(LAHDCs)%20of%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20and%20the%20constitutional%20safeguards%20that%20could%20be%20provided%20to%20ensure%20the%20measures%20and%20protection%20as%20mentioned%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20organisations%20in%20Ladakh%20had%20demanded%20a%20separate%20Union%20Territory%20for%20the%20region%20for%20decades%20and%20the%20demand%20was%20fulfilled%20on%20August%205%2C%202019.%20The%20KDA%20and%20the%20ABL%2C%20however%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20protested%20at%20different%20locations%2C%20including%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Ladakh%2C%20highlighting%20their%20key%20demands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20publishe