F689353%2F2024-02-09%2F2lvknc%2F689353%2F1707510824kuJAqb0f%2FHow_Health_Systems_Are_Navigating_The_Complexities_Of_AI_CCM_Reports.pdf%3Futm_source%3Dmedia%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_content%3DHS-navigating-complexities-AI-report-PDF-PR%26utm_campaign%3DAI-24%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2034%20US%20health%20systems%20leaders%2C%20only%2016%25%20reported%20having%20systemwide%20policies%20for%20AI%20usage%20and%20data%20access.%20And%20while%20some%20leaders%20noted%20having%20broader%20guidelines%20in%20place%20that%20could%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ealso%20apply%20to%20AI%2C%20the%20majority%20%E2%80%94%C2%A065%25%20%E2%80%94%20said%20they%20had%20no%20policies%20for%20AI%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%2C%20conducted%20by%20the%20Center%20for%20Connected%20Medicine%20at%20UPMC%C2%A0and%20KLAS%20Research%20in%20October%20and%20November%20with%20health%20systems%20of%20varying%20sizes%2C%20is%20a%20nod%20to%20the%20roadblocks%20healthcare%20is%20running%20up%20against%20as%20more%20companies%20build%20and%20sell%20AI-powered%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHealthcare%20has%20historically%20lagged%20behind%20other%20fields%20in%20adopting%20new%20technologies%2C%20though%20events%20like%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20have%20occasionally%20forced%20the%20industry's%20hand.%20However%2C%20investors%20and%20doctors%20alike%20are%20getting%20excited%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-healthcare-doctors-drugs-treatments-patients-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI's%20potential%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20healthcare%20delivery%20more%20efficient%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-burnout-ai-assistant-help-paperwork-administrative-tasks-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20burnout%20among%20medical%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20improve%20patient%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20many%20healthcare%20leaders%20aren't%20jumping%20on%20the%20AI%20bandwagon%20just%20yet.%20Some%20health%20system%20leaders%20said%20they%20haven't%20developed%20policies%20because%20the%20industry%20is%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20AI%20adoption.%20Others%20said%20they're%20waiting%20for%20federal%20regulations%20on%20AI%20before%20issuing%20their%20own%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffda-brominated-vegetable-oil-bvo-soda-proposed-ban-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFood%20and%20Drug%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20developed%20AI%20guidelines%20for%20medical%20device%20makers%2C%20the%20agency%20hasn't%20provided%20a%20broader%20framework%20for%20AI%20adoption%20or%20evaluation%20in%20healthcare.%20It%20isn't%20likely%20to%20offer%20one%20any%20time%20soon.%20FDA%20commissioner%20Robert%20Califf%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F02%2F18%2Fartificial-intelligence-health-care-fda-00141768%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%20that%20the%20agency%20doesn't%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20monitor%20the%20ever-changing%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20road%20ahead%20for%20healthcare%20AI%20startups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20public%20sector%20struggles%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20regulate%20AI%20in%20healthcare%2C%20many%20startups%20hope%20to%20harness%20the%20tech%20to%20solve%20some%20of%20the%20industry's%20biggest%20problems.%20Venture%20investors%20are%20also%20bullish%20about%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-nurses-strike-labor-union-staffing-shortage-covid-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabor%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rising%20levels%20of%20burnout%20that%20are%20driving%20some%20providers%20out%20of%20healthcare%2C%20many%20hospitals%20are%20feeling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider