ed%20the%20BJP%20of%20neglecting%20the%20development%20of%20Amethi%20and%20Raibareli%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20was%20addressing%20a%20public%20gathering%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Amethi%20during%20the%20party's%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20Congress's%20tenure%2C%20projects%20worth%20crores%20in%20Amethi%20were%20approved%20but%20most%20of%20them%20remained%20pending.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20them%20why%20the%20projects%20are%20still%20incomplete.%20They%20do%20not%20want%20to%20work%20for%20Amethi%20and%20Raibareli.%20They%20have%20finished%20off%20projects%20that%20were%20for%20Amethi%20and%20Raibareli%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20is%20conspiring%20to%20sow%20enmity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Raibareli%20and%20Amethi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20criticised%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20slogan%20of%20'Abki%20baar%2C%20400%20paar%2C'%20predicting%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20not%20surpass%20100%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20the%20BJP%20claims%20that%20it%20will%20gain%20over%20400%20seats%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20cross%20100%20seats.%20Abki%20baar%2C%20Satta%20se%20bahar%20(this%20time%2C%20they%20will%20be%20ousted%20from%20power)%26quot%3B%2C%20Kharge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%20launched%20an%20attack%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BModiji%20(PM%20Narendra%20Modi)%20would%20come%20here%20and%20accuse%20the%20Congress%20party%20of%20halting%20projects.%20Tell%20me%20what%20are%20you%20doing%20now.%20The%20public%20will%20give%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20party%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20current%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20filed%20her%20nomination%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Rajasthan.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20won%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20defeating%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20candidate%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20by%20over%201%2C65%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Amethi%20was%20represented%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20between%202004%20and%202019%2C%20he%20lost%20the%20seat%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%202019%2C%20by%20roughly%2055%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20addressing%20the%20rally%20in%20UP's%20Amethi%2C%20Kharge%20said%2C%26quot%3B...This%20is%20the%20land%20where%20Rajeev%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20ji%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20ji%20worked%20hard.%20You%20(people%20of%20Amethi)%20have%20a%20deep%20relation%20with%20them%20(Gandhi%20family).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20its%20candidate%20for%20the%20Raibareli%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20SP%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEverything%20will%20be%20alright.%20He%20has%20agreed%20and%20our%20people%20have%20agreed%20too.%20There%20is%20no%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20resumed%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Amethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20is%20on%20a%20Manipur-Mumbai%20Yatra%20covering%2015%20states%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20in%20April-May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708403700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fl50sjo6_mallikarjun-kharge_625x300_27_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-cross-100-seats-in-lok-sabha-polls-m-kharges-prediction-for-bjp-5090043%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20yesterday%20accused%20the%20