0at%2011%20am%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%2C%20convener%20of%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(non-political)%2C%20which%20is%20leading%20this%20latest%20chapter%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20along%20with%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20committee%20(KMSC)%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20was%20not%20beneficial%20for%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHence%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20reject%20it%20and%20resume%20our%20march%20from%20Wednesday%20onwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20convener%20of%20KMSC%20also%20added%20that%20they%20will%20stick%20to%20their%20demand%20of%20an%20MSP%20guarantee%20law%20on%20all%2023%20crops%20for%20which%20government%20announces%20MSP%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20said%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20was%20an%20eyewash.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fhimanshu-karan-thapar-msp-ashok-gulati-farmers%5C%22%3EBasically%2C%20it%20was%20a%20contract%20farming%20proposal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20only%20valid%20for%20those%20who%20would%20switch%20over%20from%20paddy%20or%20wheat%20to%20crops%20like%20pulses%2C%20maize%20or%20cotton.%20Contract%20farming%20as%20a%20farming%20model%20has%20already%20failed%20and%20can%E2%80%99t%20guarantee%20sustainable%20income%20to%20farmers.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20government%20proposal%20was%20for%20five%20crops%20out%20of%2023%20on%20which%20MSP%20is%20announced%20and%20it%20was%20not%20justified%20to%20leave%20those%20who%20were%20not%20part%20of%20the%20government%20proposal%20behind%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dallewal%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20farmers%20of%20the%20movement%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20have%20a%20law%20on%20the%20MSP%20and%20guaranteed%20procurement%20of%20all%2023%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20said%20various%20estimates%20by%20agriculture%20economy%20experts%20reveal%20that%20if%20the%20government%20ensures%20MSP%20for%20all%2023%20crops%2C%20total%20expenditure%20will%20not%20be%20more%20than%20Rs%201.75%20lakh%20crore.%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20spends%20almost%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20crore%20just%20on%20the%20import%20of%20edible%20oils%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20the%20government%20had%20not%20shown%20commitment%20on%20their%20other%20demands%20like%20loan%20waiver%2C%20stopping%20the%20privatisation%20of%20electricity%2C%20comprehensive%20public%20sector%20crop%20insurance%20scheme%2C%20Rs%2010%2C000%20monthly%20pension%20to%20farmers%20above%2060%20years%20of%20age%2C%20the%20dismissal%20and%20prosecution%20of%20junior%20Union%20minister%20Ajay%20Mishra%20%E2%80%98Teni%E2%80%99%20over%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20massacre%20of%20farmers%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders%20raised%20other%20matters%20like%20the%20resumption%20of%20internet%20in%20Punjab%2C%20and%20ongoing%20atrocities%20on%20farmers%20camping%20at%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20in%20Sambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20barriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpakistan-india-farmer-shambhu-medical-cost%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Being%20Treated%20as%20If%20We%20Are%20From%20Pakistan%20and%20Shambhu%20Barrier%20Is%20India-Pak%20Border%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20said%20that%20Haryana%20DGP%20in%20his%20latest%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fharyana-dgp-claims-rubber-bullets-not-pellet-guns-used-on-protesting-farmers%5C%22%3Eclaimed%20that%20pellet%20guns%20were%20not%20used%20on%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20lie%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20other%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20who%20are%20not%20part%20of%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Union%20also%20rejected%20the%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20here%2C%20the%20original%20SKM%20body%2C%20which%20is%20otherwise%20not%20part%20of%20its%20splinter%20group%20SKM%20(Non-Political)%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20march%20programme%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20to%20procure%20five%20crops%20namely%20Maize%2C%20Cotton%2C%20Arhar%2FTur%2C%20Massur%20and%20Urad%20for%20five%20years%20was%20basically%20to%20divert%20and%20dilute%20the%20demand%20of%20MSP%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98cost%20%2B%2050%25%20profit%E2%80%99%20model%20for%20all%20crops%20with%20guaranteed%20procurement%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20promised%20in%20the%20BJP%20manifesto%20ahead%20of%20the%202014%20general%20election%20and%20originally%20recommended%20by%20National%20Farmers%20Commission%20chaired%20by%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20and%20submitted%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20declared%20that%20nothing%20below%20the%20abovementioned%20MSP%20model%20for%20all%20crops%20with%20guaranteed%20procurement%20is%20acceptable%20to%20the%20farmers%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20unable%20to%20implement%20the%20promise%20made%20by%20BJP%2C%20then%20let%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20be%20honest%20to%20tell%20that%20to%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20showdown%20likely%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClashes%20had%20begun%20and%20dozens%20were%20injured%20when%20farmers%20were%20halted%20from%20marching%20towards%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%20at%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20borders%20at%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20status%20quo%20as%20farmers%20have%20been%20in%20constant%20talks%20with%20the%20Centre.%20There%20have%20been%20four%20round%20of%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2010%2C000%20farmers%20have%20been%20camping%20on%20these%20borders%20where%20security%20personnel%20too%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20huge%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20press%20conference%20on%20Monday%2C%20farmers%20leaders%20appealed%20to%20the%20Haryana%20government%20not%20to%20halt%20their%20march%20and%20allow%20them%20to%20camp%20at%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20the%20fulfilment%20of%20their%20legitimate%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20said%20that%20the%20agitation%20for%20their%20demand%20is%20farmers%E2%80%99%20constitutional%20right%20and%20cannot%20be%20taken%20away%20by%20force%2C%20as%20it%20is%20happening%20at%20these%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708400661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141152%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-08-at-1.00.13-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-reject-centres-proposal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Basically%2C%20it%20was%20a%20contract%20farming%20proposal.%20It%20was%20only%20valid%20for%20those%20who%20would%20switch%20over%20from%20paddy%20or%20wheat%20to%20crops%20like%20pulses%2C%20maize%20or%20cotton%2C'%20one%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20farmers'%20movement%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-reject-centres-proposal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Widow%2C%20ex-prime%20minister%20and%20former%20police%20chief%20indicted%20in%202021%20assassination%20of%20Haiti's%20president%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708400442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107838317%2Cimgsize-164746.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwidow-ex-prime-minister-and-former-police-chief-indicted-in-2021-assassination-of-haitis-president%2Farticleshow%2F107838317.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesof