e%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20has%20reached%20a%20critical%20point%2C%20more%20recently%20we%20had%20an%20alarming%2035%20teachers%20absent%2C%20underscoring%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20challenges%20we%20are%20facing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20of%20the%20committee's%20seven%20members%20signed%20the%20letter%2C%20which%20was%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wcvb.com%2Farticle%2Fcall-for-national-guard-help-brockton-high-school-security%2F46855550%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoston-based%20ABC%20affiliate%20WCVB-TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20members%20said%20Brockton%20didn't%20have%20enough%20staff%20to%20monitor%20hallways%20and%20school%20exits%2C%20allowing%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bnoticeable%20increase%26quot%3B%20in%20truancy%20and%20trespassing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstances%20of%20students%20wandering%20the%20halls%2C%20engaging%20in%20altercations%2C%20and%20causing%20disruptions%20in%20classrooms%20have%20become%20alarmingly%20frequent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20members%20asked%20Gov.%20Maura%20Healey%20for%20a%20meeting%20to%20discuss%20the%20temporary%20deployment%20of%20the%20National%20Guard%2C%20hoping%20to%20rely%20on%20its%20%26quot%3Bexpertise%20in%20crisis%20management%26quot%3B%20to%20prevent%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20tragedy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENational%20Guard%20can%20be%20used%20as%20hall%20monitors%20or%20substitute%20teachers%2C%20a%20committee%20member%20said%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fboston25%2Fstatus%2F1759621650000282109%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20press%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20about%20their%20call%20for%20help%2C%20the%20committee%20members%20said%20the%20local%20mayor%2C%20Robert%20Sullivan%2C%20had%20received%20the%20letter%20and%20forwarded%20it%20to%20Healey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20asking%20them%20to%20deploy%20a%20whole%20army%20to%20our%20school.%20We're%20asking%20for%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20committee%20member%20Ana%20Oliver.%20%26quot%3BEspecially%20with%20the%20teacher%20shortage%20throughout%20the%20Commonwealth%20of%20Massachusetts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20something%20that%20is%20negative%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20committee%20member%20Tony%20Rodrigues.%20%26quot%3BThe%20National%20Guard%20does%20bring%20positivity%2C%20we%20use%20them%20to%20deploy%20COVID%20vaccinations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERodrigues%20suggested%20that%20National%20Guard%20service%20members%20or%20staff%20be%20deployed%20as%20hall%20monitors%20and%20substitute%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaudio%20Gomes%2C%20another%20committee%20member%2C%20said%20the%20four%20weren't%20necessarily%20asking%20to%20bring%20armed%20soldiers%20into%20classrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20the%20first%20thought%20that%20comes%20to%20mind%20when%20you%20hear%20'National%20Guard'%20is%20uniform%20and%20arms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gomes.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20not%20the%20case.%20They're%20people%20like%20us.%20They're%20educated.%20They're%20trained%2C%20and%20we%20just%20need%20their%20assistance%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESome%20officials%20and%20parents%20disagree%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20urgent%20request%20has%20received%20pushback%20from%20some%20local%20officials%20and%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSoldiers%20in%20military%20field%20uniforms%20aren't%20the%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20Brockton%20City%20Councilor%20Winthrop%20Farwell%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3Dpfbid02d4MRvRJNxYRryeR4CP1wSFgByHtJZ8ZM2bFem3Qjt1jRGJVwapHEb21oZ9NwavUrl%26id%3D100064932420374%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20on%20Facebook%20on%20Saturday%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20the%20committee%20should%20solve%20the%20issue%20