eps%20Out%20Of%20The%20Shadows%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStony-faced%20and%20resolute%2C%20Yulia%20Navalnaya%20on%20Monday%20picked%20up%20the%20baton%20from%20her%20late%20husband%20Alexei%20with%20a%20call%20to%20action%20for%20Russia's%20opposition%20after%20years%20in%20his%20shadow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20dimly%20lit%20room%2C%20her%20light%20blond%20hair%20tied%20in%20her%20usual%20bun%2C%20the%2047-year-old%20addressed%20the%20opposition%20that%20has%20been%20left%20leaderless%20after%20Navalny's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20call%20on%20you%20to%20stand%20by%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20powerful%20nine-minute%20video%20that%20gathered%20around%20two%20and%20a%20half%20million%20views%20in%20a%20few%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20husband%20has%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20been%20Putin's%20most%20prolific%20critic%2C%20running%20against%20the%20long-time%20ruler%20and%20blasting%20the%20regime's%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20met%20on%20holiday%20in%20Turkey%2C%20with%20both%20saying%20they%20fell%20in%20love%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20trained%20economist%2C%20Navalnaya%20gave%20up%20her%20job%20to%20raise%20the%20couple's%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20stayed%20away%20from%20media%20spotlight%2C%20maintaining%20as%20much%20privacy%20as%20she%20could%20while%20Alexei's%20political%20career%20took%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20stood%20by%20him%20as%20he%20galvanised%20mass%20protests%20in%20Russia%2C%20flying%20with%20him%20out%20of%20the%20country%20as%20he%20lay%20in%20a%20coma%20after%20a%20poisoning%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20months%20later%2C%20she%20was%20defiant%20when%20the%20couple%20flew%20back%20to%20Moscow%2C%20knowing%20it%20would%20land%20him%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaiter%2C%20bring%20us%20some%20vodka%2C%20we're%20flying%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Navalnaya%20said%20in%20a%20video%20sitting%20next%20to%20Alexei%20on%20the%20plane%2