az%20has%20shown%20that%20he%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20Indian%20team.%20The%2026-year-old%20got%20his%20Test%20cap%20after%20years%20of%20toiling%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%20and%20also%20honing%20his%20skills%20at%20his%20father's%20'Macho%20Cricket%20Club'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hard%20work%20and%20systematic%20planning%20of%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20two%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%2C%20paid%20off%20against%20the%20likes%20of%20Tom%20Hartley%2C%20Joe%20Root%20and%20Rehan%20Ahmed%20in%20Rajkot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20taken%20playing%20500%20deliveries%20per%20day%20from%20off%2C%20leg%20and%20left-arm%20spinners%20across%20Oval%2C%20Cross%20and%20Azad%20Maidans%20in%20Mumbai%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20coach%20who%20has%20seen%20the%20Mumbaikar's%20growth%20from%20close%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...during%20(COVID)%20lockdown%2C%20he%20undertook%20a%20car%20journey%20covering%201600km.%20From%20Mumbai%20to%20Amroha%2C%20Moradabad%2C%20Meerut%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Mathura%20and%20Dehradun%2C%20he%20travelled%20and%20played%20on%20proverbial%20'akhadas'%20where%20the%20ball%20turns%20square%20with%20one%20shooting%20up%20and%20few%20staying%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sarfaraz%20that%20was%20manoeuvering%20the%20spinners%20with%20ease%2C%20honed%20his%20skills%20the%20tough%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20credit%20for%20the%20final%20product%20lies%20not%20just%20with%20Naushad%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoaches%20of%20Bhuvneshwar%20Kumar%20(Sanjay%20Rastogi)%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%20(Badruddin%20Sheikh)%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20(Kapil%20Deo%20Pandey)%2C%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20(Sanjay%20Bhardwaj)%20and%20father%20of%20India%20A%20captain%20Abhimanyu%20Easwaran%20(RP%20Easwaran)%20have%20also%20contributed%20in%20their%20little%20way%20to%20make%20Sarfaraz%20a%20finished%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20all%20arranged%20for%20Sarfaraz's%20net%20sessions%20against%20spinners%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20COVID%20lockdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20lockdown%2C%20Naushad%20called%20me%20as%20we%20are%20both%20from%20Azamgarh%20and%20we%20played%20club%20cricket%20in%20Mumbai%20when%20I%20was%20employed%20with%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%20So%2C%20when%20he%20wanted%20his%20son%20to%20get%20practice%2C%20I%20felt%20it's%20my%20duty%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapil%20Pandey%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20lockdown%2C%20Sarfaraz%20played%20Kuldeep%20a%20lot%20at%20our%20Kanpur%20Academy.%20They%20did%20lot%20of%20net%20sessions%20together.%20I%20would%20arrange%20T20%20matches%20as%20that%20season%2C%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20T20%20was%20main%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20grown%20up%20playing%20on%20Mumbai's%20red%20soil%2C%20Sarfaraz%20has%20the%20perfect%20game%20against%20spin%20and%20uses%20his%20feet%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami's%20coach%20Badruddin%20also%20spoke%20about%20his%20part%20in%20helping%20Sarfaraz%20attain%20mastery%20of%20spin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20arranged%20for%20his%20training%20and%20nets%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20No%20doubt%20both%20the%20father%20and%20son%20worked%20hard.%20I%20arranged%20for%20his%20stay%20in%20a%20hostel%20and%20got%20him%20to%20play%20a%20number%20of%20games.%26quot%3B%20Another%20coach%20who%20has%20seen%20Naushad%20train%20his%20sons%20--%20Sarfaraz%20and%20India%20U-19%20star%20Musheer%20--%20spoke%20about%20the%20gruelling%20training%20regimen%20that%20the%20two%20players%20endured%20even%20on%20non-match%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20young%20age%2C%20he%20has%20been%20playing%20hundreds%20of%20balls.%20So%20when%20Mumbai%20didn't%20have%20a%20match%2C%20Naushad%20prepared%20an%20astro%20turf%20wicket%20at%20home%20where%20Sarfaraz%20practised%20against%20pacers.%20But%20the%20moment%20he%20has%20to%20play%20spin%2C%20they%20go%20to%20the%20Maidans%20and%20do%20open%20field%2