ption%20to%20covert%20illegitimate%20influence%20over%20decision-making%20irrespective%20of%20the%20manner%20of%20financial%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20rendered%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20particularly%20pernicious%20was%20their%20architecture%20designed%20to%20provide%20two%20unique%20advantages%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%3A%20shielding%20unlimited%20corporate%20donations%20to%20its%20own%20account%20from%20public%20scrutiny%20while%20rendering%20donations%20to%20all%20other%20political%20parties%20transparent%20to%20the%20Central%20government%20thus%20exposing%20supporters%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20retributive%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20other%20than%20this%20selective%20transparency%20designed%20to%20benefit%20the%20BJP%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20offer%20no%20gains%20over%20the%20stipulation%20that%20donations%20over%20a%20set%20threshold%20be%20made%20electronically.%20Unsurprisingly%2C%20the%20BJP%20cornered%20the%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20all%20electoral%20bonds.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20attempted%20to%20fix%20this%20anomaly%20of%20selective%20transparency%20by%20mandating%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20make%20public%20relevant%20details%20of%20all%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-primacy-vote-over-note%5C%22%3EThe%20SC%E2%80%99s%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Judgement%20Affirms%20the%20Primacy%20of%20the%20Vote%20Over%20the%20Note%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20must%20be%20acknowledged%20that%20electoral%20bonds%20represented%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20political%20funding.%20The%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%20also%20holds%20the%20most%20expensive%20national%20elections%20spending%20an%20estimated%20%248.7%20billion%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20alone.%20Yet%20electoral%20bonds%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%20account%20for%20only%20about%20%242%20billion.%20The%20big%20picture%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20is%20thus%20not%20their%20impact%20on%20cleaning%20up%20political%20funding%20but%20the%20endgame%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20under-appreciated%20aspect%20of%20mainstream%20electoral%20politics%20is%20the%20centrality%20of%20pure%20hardcore%20logistics%20in%20running%20a%20political%20party.%20A%20political%20party%20must%20build%20organisation%20and%20mobilise%20the%20electorate%20across%20the%20length%20and%20depth%20of%20its%20electoral%20footprint.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20meetings%20have%20to%20be%20organised%2C%20grounds%20booked%2C%20people%20mobilised%2C%20distances%20covered%2C%20meals%20distributed%2C%20pamphlets%20printed%2C%20volunteers%20identified%20and%20sustained%20through%20various%20tangible%20and%20intangible%20benefits.%20All%20of%20this%20costs%20money.%20Yet%20there%20are%20limited%20sources%20for%20political%20parties%20to%20raise%20funds%20ranging%20from%20earnings%20from%20their%20own%20assets%20like%20fixed%20deposits%2C%20properties%2C%20membership%20fees%20and%20donations%20of%20various%20kinds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20country%20where%2080%20crore%20people%20receive%20free%20food%20grain%20and%20without%20wider%20politicisation%20of%20the%20electorate%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20for%20political%20parties%20to%20sustainably%20raise%20funds%20from%20the%20people%20at%20large.%20Thus%2C%20while%20there%20are%20many%20personally%20honest%20politicians%2C%20corruption%20is%20baked%20into%20the%20institutional%20architecture%20of%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20obvious%20that%20this%20kind%20of%20structural%20corruption%20cannot%20be%20fixed%20by%20tinkering%20at%20the%20margins%20of%20funding%20or%20by%20going%20after%20individuals.%20It%20is%20also%20evident%20that%20no%20political%20party%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20BJP%2C%20by%20far%20the%20richest%20political%20party%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20can%20be%20immune%20to%20this%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20of%20corruption%20is%20thus%20not%20about%20corruption%20at%20all%20but%20about%20neutralising%20the%20opposition%20and%20tilting%20the%20scales%20in%20its%20favour%20in%20an%20increasingly%20uneven%20contest.%20This%20is%20borne%20out%20too%20by%20the%20weaponisation%20of%20Central%20agencies%20against%20those%20standing%20in%20opposition%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20not%20least%20the%20four-fold%20jump%20since%202014%20in%20ED%20cases%20against%20politicians%2C%2095%25%C2%A0%20of%20which%20are%20from%20opposition%20ranks.%20In%20fact%2C%20given%20the%20nexus%20between%20money%20and%20electoral%20politics%2C%20anti-corruption%20campaigns%20by%20mainstream%20political%20parties%20are%20almost%20never%20in%20good%20faith%20and%20have%20instead%20been%20deployed%20globally%20by%20strongmen%20leaders%20to%20fix%20internal%20and%20external%20opponents%20and%20weaken%20institutional%20curbs%20on%20their%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20BJP%20supporters%20concede%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20concerted%20and%20motivated%20action%20against%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20it%20is%20sometimes%20dismissed%20as%20having%20a%20limited%20impact%20on%20public%20interest%20given%20the%20endemic%20nature%20of%20corruption%20in%20our%20political%20architecture.%20This%20is%20a%20highly%20problematic%20summation%20given%20that%20democracy%20is%20first%20and%20foremost%20about%20an%20even%20contest%20between%20a%20plurality%20of%20choices.%20It%20is%20for%20the%20voter%20to%20determine%20the%20relative%20quality%20of%20available%20choices%20and%20any%20artificial%20restriction%20on%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choices%20is%20itself%20an%20attack%20on%20democracy.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20many%20of%20these%20same%20politicians%20have%20found%20welcome%20%E2%80%93%20and%20respite%20from%20Central%20agencies%20%E2%80%93%20in%20joining%20the%20BJP%20making%20it%20clear%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20pursuit%20is%20power%20by%20any%20means%20and%20not%20probity%20in%20public%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fquid-pro-quo-how-revealing-electoral-bonds-will-clear-questions-of-len-den%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Quid-Pro-Quo%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20Revealing%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Will%20Clear%20Questions%20of%20%E2%80%98Len-Den%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20even%20as%20we%20argue%20that%20democracy%20is%20defined%20by%20an%20open%20contest%20between%20multiple%20competing%20alternatives%20and%20that%20it%20is%20for%20the%20voter%20to%20determine%20the%20relative%20quality%20of%20those%20alternatives%2C%20endemic%20corruption%20is%20also%20another%20kind%20of%20abridgement%20of%20democracy.%20Corruption%20too%20limits%20voters%E2%80%99%20choice%20by%20entrenching%20incumbents%2C%20weakening%20the%20capacity%20of%20honest%20politicians%20to%20assert%20themselves%20and%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20new%20political%20formations%20to%20emerge.%20However%2C%20our%20politics%20cannot%20be%20cleaned%20up%20through%20moral%20outrage%20or%20motivated%20action%20against%20individual%20leaders%2C%20or%20casual%20contempt%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esab%20chor%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Corruption%20in%20politics%20is%20also%20resistant%20to%20simple%20one-point%20reforms%20because%20of%20the%20complex%20architecture%20of%20power.%20The%20way%20forward%20thus%20requires%20us%20to%20think%20more%20expansively%20and%20holistically%20about%20how%20we%20should%20structure%20and%20sustain%20our%20core%20political%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERuchi%20Gupta%20writes%20about%20democracy%2C%20tech%2C%20public%20discourse%20and%20contestations%20for%20power%20in%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20Substack%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0India%3A%20Politics%2C%20Power%20%26amp%3B%20Public%20Discourse.%C2%A0%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%