ues)%20two%20days%20before%20the%20match%20and%20how%20much%20can%20we%20do%20anyway%20in%20two%20days%3F%20%E2%80%9CThe%20curators%20decide%20and%20make%20the%20pitch.%20We%20have%20the%20strength%20to%20play%20on%20any%20wicket%20and%20win%20on%20it.%20When%20we%20won%20the%20Test%20in%20South%20Africa%20(at%20Cape%20Town)%2C%20everyone%20knows%20what%20kind%20of%20wicket%20it%20was%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20said%20the%20Indian%20team%20has%20found%20a%20way%20through%20all%20conditions%20witnessed%20in%20the%20first%20three%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C(In)%20the%20last%20three%20Tests%20we%20played%2C%20there%20were%20different%20challenges.%20In%20the%20first%20Test%20(Hyderabad)%2C%20the%20ball%20was%20spinning%20and%20the%20pitch%20was%20slow.%20In%20Vizag%2C%20it%20was%20(keeping)%20low.%20As%20the%20game%20progressed%2C%20the%20wicket%20became%20slower.%20Here%2C%20it%20played%20well%20for%20the%20first%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20saw%20that%20the%20ball%20was%20turning%20and%20it%20was%20low.%20This%20is%20(in)%20the%20nature%20(of%20pitches)%2C%20we%20get%20pitches%20like%20these%20in%20India.%20But%20if%20we%20get%20rank%20turners%2C%20we%20will%20play%20on%20them%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20skipper%20said%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20has%20acquired%20enough%20experience%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20that%20the%20team%20management%20did%20not%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20have%20discussed%20any%20plans%20with%20him%20before%20he%20made%20his%20debut%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20haven't%20seen%20Sarfaraz%20bat%20that%20much.%20But%20all%20the%20people%20I've%20heard%20from%2C%20the%20players%20who%20are%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20(that)%20he's%20made%20runs%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20difficult%20situations%20for%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe's%20hungry%20for%20runs%20and%20for%20the%20last%204-5%20years%2C%20he's%20continuously%20made%20runs%20in%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20so%20(that%20means)%20he's%20doing%20something%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn't%20discuss%20any%20plans%20with%20him.%20Because%20I%20know%20that%20if%20you%20let%20him%20be%2C%20he'll%20do%20his%20your%20job%2C%20which%20I've%20heard%20from%20the%20players%20from%20Mumbai%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708395720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fpj32e1e8_rohit-sharma-bcci_625x300_19_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fye-aajkal-ke-bacche-rohit-sharmas-post-for-team-india-trio-breaks-the-internet-5082076%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20shared%20a%20special%20social%20media%20post%20for%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20after%20India's%20434-run%20win%20against%20England%20in%20Rajkot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20pushes%20for%20UN%20to%20support%20temporary%20Gaza%20ceasefire%2C%20oppose%20Rafah%20assault%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708395660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107835988%2Cimgsize-1029011.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-pushes-for-un-to-support-temporary-gaza-ceasefire-oppose-rafah-assault%2Farticleshow%2F107835840.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107835840.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-pushe