on-agenda-5090820%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20Hack%20The%20Brain%2C%20Recalling%20Specific%20Memories%20With%20Prosthetics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EImagine%20a%20world%20where%20forgotten%20memories%20are%20brought%20back%20with%20the%20touch%20of%20a%20button.%20This%20isn't%20science%20fiction%3B%20it's%20the%20cutting%20edge%20of%20prosthetics%20and%20neural%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20life-changing%20devices%20help%20individuals%20with%20disabilities%20regain%20their%20independence.%20Prosthetics%20offer%20a%20second%20chance%2C%20replacing%20missing%20limbs%20and%20restoring%20movement.%20But%20researchers%20are%20pushing%20boundaries%20further%20with%20neural%20prosthetics%2C%20directly%20connecting%20with%20the%20nervous%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20remarkable%20feat%2C%20scientists%20from%20Wake%20Forest%20University%20School%20of%20Medicine%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%20(USC)%20used%20a%20neural%20prosthetic%20to%20unlock%20specific%20memories.%20Imagine%20struggling%20to%20recall%20a%20loved%20one's%20face%2C%20then%20suddenly%2C%20with%20a%20gentle%20electrical%20nudge%2C%20the%20memory%20floods%20back.%20This%20breakthrough%20study%2C%20led%20by%20Dr%20Robert%20Hampson%2C%20offers%20hope%20for%20treating%20memory%20loss%20due%20to%20age%2C%20injury%2C%20or%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20technology%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20stages%2C%20but%20the%20possibilities%20are%20mind-boggling.%20Imagine%20restoring%20movement%20to%20paralyzed%20limbs%2C%20or%20enhancing%20our%20senses%20beyond%20what%20nature%20allows.%20The%20future%20where%20disabilities%20are%20not%20limitations%2C%20but%20opportunities%20for%20enhancement%2C%20is%20closer%20than%20ever%20before.%20In%20this%20future%2C%20prosthetics%20and%20neural%20technology%20won't%20just%20restore%20what's%20lost%2C%20they'll%20open%20doors%20to%20a%20world%20of%20extraordinary%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20appear%20online%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffncom.2024.1263311%2Ffull%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFrontiers%20in%20Computational%20Neuroscience.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%2C%20we%20not%20only%20highlight%20an%20innovative%20technique%20for%20neurostimulation%20to%20enhance%20memory%2C%20but%20we%20also%20demonstrate%20that%20stimulating%20memory%20isn't%20just%20limited%20to%20a%20general%20approach%20but%20can%20also%20be%20applied%20to%20specific%20information%20that%20is%20critical%20to%20a%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.wakehealth.edu%2Fnews-releases%2F2024%2F02%2Fneural-prosthetic-device-can-help-humans-restore-memory%5C%22%3Esaid%20Brent%20Roeder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20PhD%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20in%20the%20department%20of%20translational%20neuroscience%20at%20Wake%20Forest%20University%20School%20of%20Medicine%20and%20the%20study's%20corresponding%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20implanted%20electrodes%20in%2014%20epilepsy%20patients%20to%20test%20memory%20stimulation.%20During%20image%20recognition%20tasks%2C%20some%20participants%20received%20electrical%20stimulation%20(MDM)%20which%20led%20to%20improved%20memory%20in%2022%25%20of%20cases.%20Notably%2C%20almost%2040%25%20of%20those%20with%20pre-existing%20memory%20problems%20saw%20significant%20gains%20when%20stimulated%20on%20both%20brain%20sides.%20This%20research%20offers%20a%20promising%20glimpse%20into%20using%20MDM%20for%20memory%20enhancement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20an%20intervention%20that%20can%20restore%20memory%20function%20that's%20lost%20because%20of%20Alzheimer's%20disease%2C%20stroke%20or%20head%20injury%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Roeder%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20found%20the%20most%20pronounced%20change%20occurred%20in%20people%20who%20had%20impaired%20memory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2