-touches-kirron-khers-feet-as-they-meet-for-a-lunch-outing%2Farticleshow%2F107835323.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107835323.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAnil%20Kapoor%20bonds%20with%20Anupam%20Kher%2C%20Kirron%20Kher%2C%20Kanwal%2C%20Jatinder%20Pannu%20at%20a%20lunch%20hosted%20by%20Abhinav%20Bindra.%20Anil%20seeks%20Kirron's%20blessing.%20Kirron%20shares%20about%20the%20gathering.%20Anil%20produces%20a%20biopic%20on%20Abhinav%20Bindra's%20journey%20starring%20Harsh%20Varrdhan.%20The%20movie%20is%20planned%20to%20release%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanil-kapoor-touches-kirron-khers-feet-as-they-meet-for-a-lunch-outing%2Farticleshow%2F107835323.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20A%20First%2C%20Crew%20Abandons%20Ship%20In%20Red%20Sea%20After%20Houthi%20Missile%20Strikes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20of%20a%20commercial%20ship%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20abandoned%20the%20vessel%20following%20a%20Houthi%20attack%20-%20the%20first%20such%20evacuation%20since%20the%20militant%20group%20began%20menacing%20trade%20in%20the%20vital%20waterway%20late%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo-anti%20ship%20ballistic%20missiles%20damaged%20the%20Belize-flagged%20Rubymar%20on%20Sunday%20evening%20local%20time%2C%20US%20Central%20Command%20said%20Monday%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%20A%20coalition%20warship%20and%20another%20merchant%20ship%20responded%20to%20the%20distress%20call%2C%20and%20the%20Rubymar's%20crew%20were%20transported%20to%20a%20nearby%20port%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20November%2C%20the%20Houthis%20have%20escalated%20their%20attacks%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Yemen%20with%20missiles%20and%20drone%20strikes%20on%20the%20merchant%20fleet.%20The%20Iran-backed%20group%20says%20they%20are%20targeting%20ships%20with%20links%20to%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20-%20their%20response%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20western%20airstrikes%20that%20have%20sought%20to%20quell%20the%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rubymar%20is%20a%20relatively%20small%20cargo%20ship.%20Its%20registered%20owner%20is%20in%20Southampton%2C%20England%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Equasis%20international%20maritime%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Houthi%20spokesman%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20an%20attack%20on%20an%20unidentified%20British%20ship%20resulted%20in%20its%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20sinking%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20claim%20that%20could%20not%20be%20verified%20independently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentcom%20didn't%20mention%20in%20its%20statement%20whether%20the%20Rubymar%20had%20sunk%2C%20and%20the%20vessel's%20owner%20didn't%20respond%20to%20an%20earlier%20request%20for%20comment.%20UK%20Maritime%20Trade%20Operations%20had%20no%20further%20updates%20on%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20company%20official%20at%20GMZ%20Ship%20Management%20Co.%20in%20Lebanon%20said%20the%20attacks%20on%20the%20vessel%20occurred%20in%20the%20engine%20room%20and%20the%20front%20of%20the%20ship.%20There%20were%20no%20reports%20of%20injuries%20to%20the%20crew%2C%20who%20were%20being%20taken%20to%20Djibouti%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2012%25%20of%20global%20trade%20-%20and%20as%20much%20as%2030%25%20of%20container%20traffic%20-%20passes%20through%20the%20Suez%20Canal%2C%20at%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20each%20year.%20In%20order%20to%20avoid%20the%20attacks%2C%20a%20significant%20percentage%20of%20the%20world's%20oil%20and%20gas%20carriers%2C%20bulk%20commodity%20ships%20and%20container%20vessels%20are%20now%20sailing%20thousands%20of%20miles%20around%20Africa%2C%20adding%20to%20voyage%20times%20and%20boosting%20costs%20to%20world%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20on%20Monday%2C%20another%20ship%20reported%20two%20nearby%20explosions%2C%20with%20evidence%20of%20shrapnel%20and%20damage%20to%20paintwork%2C%20though%20it%20continued%20to%20its%20next%20port%20of%20call.%20Maritime%20intelligence%20company%20Ambrey%20described%20the%20ship%20as%20a%20Greece-flagged%20bulk%20commodity%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Houthis%20said%20in%20their%20statement%20that%20they%20had%20also%20targeted%20two%20other%20vessels%2C%20though%20specific%20details%20couldn't%20immediately%20be%20verified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20formally%20launched%20a%20defensive%20naval%20operation%20Monday%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20commercial%20vessels%20from%20Houthi%20attacks.%20The%20mission%2C%20commanded%20by%20Greece%2C%20will%20accompany%20some%20ships%20and%20protect%20them%20against%20attacks%20from%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20to%20the%20Persian%20Gulf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20weekend%2C%20the%20US%20said%20it%20conducted%20five%20self-defense%20strikes%20against%20the%20Houthis%2C%20including%20one%20against%20an%20underwater%20vessel.%20Central%20Command%20said%20it%20was%20the%20first%20observed%20deployment%20of%20subsea%20attack%20capability%20since%20the%20attacks%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708391820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fpr4n5o3c_houthi-rebels_625x300_26_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-a-first-crew-abandons-ship-in-red-sea-after-houthi-missile-strikes-5090850%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20crew%20of%20a%20commercial%20ship%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20abandoned%20the%20vessel%20following%20a%20Houthi%20attack%20-%20the%20first%20such%20evacuation%20since%20the