0her%20two%20children.%20But%20her%20husband%2C%20Bablu%20Prajapati%2C%20always%20encouraged%20her%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20had%20seen%20before%20marriage%20was%20our%20village.%20My%20husband%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339969%2Fadil-qadri-attar-perfumes-shark-tank-india-entrepreneur-asthma-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewanted%20me%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20participate%20in%20matters%20of%20local%20governance%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saroj%20shares%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20an%20opportunity%20presented%20itself%20to%20contribute%20to%20her%20community%2C%20she%20grabbed%20it%2C%20and%C2%A0%20served%20as%20the%20village%20sarpanch%20for%20eight%20years.%20During%20her%20tenure%2C%20she%20met%20many%20women%20from%20rural%20areas%20and%20learnt%20about%20their%20financial%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20then%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20help%20provide%20an%20income%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20stepped%20down%2C%20she%20became%20busy%20discharging%20duties%20at%20home.%20Soon%2C%20both%20her%20children%20left%20for%20college%20and%20she%20was%20left%20with%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20build%20something.%20She%20got%20the%20answer%20for%20her%20%E2%80%98what%20to%20do%E2%80%99%20after%20watching%20the%20two%20women%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20it%20so%20happened%20that%20his%20mother%20was%20making%20pickles%20at%20the%20time%20as%20mangoes%20were%20in%20season.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20relative%20or%20friend%20who%20comes%20home%20during%20the%20mango%20season%20always%20takes%20a%20pickle%20jar%20home.%20Everyone%20who%20tastes%20it%20becomes%20a%20fan.%20I%20thought%20that%20this%20would%20be%20a%20perf