tical%20influence%20%E2%80%93%20the%20next%20best%20thing%20for%20them%20to%20a%20third%20term%20for%20Jokowi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20major%20political%20shake-up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20a%20large%20block%20of%20votes%20that%20had%20previously%20gone%20to%20Jokowi%20shifted%20to%20Prabowo%2C%20ensuring%20his%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20Jokowi%20is%20a%20member%20of%20former%20president%20Megawati%20Soekarnoputri%E2%80%99s%20PDI-P%20party%2C%20his%20supporters%20would%20normally%20have%20backed%20PDI-P%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20Ganjar.%20But%20Jokowi%20sabotaged%20Ganjar%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20by%20implicitly%20supporting%20his%20rival%2C%20leaving%20Ganjar%20to%20run%20a%20distant%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20indications%20suggest%20that%20while%20PDI-P%20will%20remain%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20national%20legislature%2C%20its%20share%20of%20the%20vote%20may%20slide%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnasional.kompas.com%2Fread%2F2024%2F02%2F14%2F20084391%2Fquick-count-pileg-2024-litbang-kompas-data-40-persen-pdi-p-golkar-gerindra%23google_vignette%5C%22%3E20%25%20to%2018%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20matters%20because%20the%20next-biggest%20parties%20look%20to%20be%20two%20that%20backed%20Prabowo%E2%80%93Golkar%20and%20Gerindra.%20Both%20received%20around%2014%25%20of%20the%20vote%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cquick%20count%E2%80%9D%2C%20up%20from%20the%20last%20election%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20Jokowi%20has%20delivered%20a%20humiliating%20blow%20to%20Megawati%20and%20her%20party%2C%20which%20many%20will%20see%20as%20pay-back%20for%20Megawati%E2%80%99s%20arrogant%20treatment%20of%20Jokowi%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2FBL-SEAB-5976%5C%22%3Emere%20%E2%80%9Cparty%20functionary%E2%80%9D%20during%20his%20time%20in%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20particularly%20galling%20outcome%20for%20Megawati%2C%20as%20Prabowo%20was%20her%20running%20mate%20when%20she%20lost%20the%20presidential%20election%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20controversies%20behind%20the%20Prabowo%20campaign%2C%20the%20losers%20are%20likely%20to%20challenge%20the%20result%20in%20the%20Constitutional%20Court.%20This%20is%20common%20after%20elections%20in%20Indonesia%20and%20sometimes%20leads%20to%20recounts%20and%20even%20re-voting%20in%20some%20electorates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Prabowo%E2%80%99s%20huge%20lead%20means%20an%20upset%20is%20unlikely.%20And%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20bother-in-law%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20nine%20judges%20on%20the%20Constitutional%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20can%20we%20expect%20from%20the%20new%20president%3F%20First%2C%20Prabowo%20will%20not%20take%20over%20immediately.%20Under%20the%20Indonesian%20system%2C%20he%20must%20wait%20until%20October%20to%20be%20sworn%20in.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20Jokowi%20will%20remain%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20the%20next%20eight%20months%20will%20be%20a%20time%20of%20intense%20horse-trading%2C%20pay-offs%20and%20political%20deals%2C%20as%20the%20political%20and%20business%20elite%20%E2%80%93%20including%20Jokowi%20%E2%80%93%20manoeuvre%20to%20build%20a%20new%20regime%20and%20secure%20their%20places%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOligarchs%20who%20backed%20Prabowo%E2%80%99s%20campaigns%20can%20expect%20to%20have%20cabinet%20seats%20and%20lucrative%20appointments%20given%20to%20them%20or%20their%20supporters%2C%20while%20Prabowo%E2%80%99s%20rivals%20will%20have%20to%20be%20placated%20or%20isolated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20negotiations%20will%20take%20some%20time%2C%20not%20least%20because%20Megawati%20and%20her%20PDI-P%20will%20still%20be%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with.%20Prabowo%20will%20probably%20work%20with%20Jokowi%20to%20try%20to%20recreate%20the%20sort%20of%20grand%20alliance%20of%20parties%20that%20Jokowi%20constructed%20to%20control%20the%20national%20legislature.%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20PDI-P%20may%20choose%20to%20go%20into%20opposition.%20This%20would%20force%20Prabowo%20to%20make%20a%20major%20political%20recalibration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20democratic%20regression%20that%20marked%20Jokowi%E2%80%99s%20decade%20in%20office%20is%20only%20likely%20to%20increase%20under%20Prabowo.%20Under%20Jokowi%2C%20core%20democratic%20institutions%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Findonesia-s-popular-president-accused-of-undermining-democracy-%2F7482068.html%5C%22%3EConstitutional%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feastasiaforum.org%2F2021%2F03%2F16%2Findonesias-corruption-eradication-commission-in-dire-straits%2F%5C%22%3EAnti-Corruption%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20(KPK)%20were%20undermined%2C%20restrictions%20on%20freedom%20of%20speech%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2022%2F12%2F19%2F1144064811%2Findonesia-has-updated-its-criminal-code-with-a-raft-of-free-speech-restrictions%5C%22%3Estrengthened%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20critics%20of%20the%20government%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findonesiaatmelbourne.unimelb.edu.au%2Findonesia-is-one-of-the-worlds-largest-democracies-but-its-weaponising-defamation-laws-to-smother-dissent%2F%5C%22%3Etargeted%20for%20prosecution%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20was%20reticent%20during%20the%20campaign%2C%20Prabowo%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channelnewsasia.com%2Fcommentary%2Findonesia-presidential-election-prabowo-democracy-term-limits-opposition-4085111%5C%22%3Every%20clear%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20that%20he%20thinks%20the%20democratic%20reforms%20that%20followed%20the%20fall%20of%20Soeharto%20in%201998%2C%20should%20be%20wound%20back.%20He%20is%20unlikely%20to%20do%20this%20immediately%2C%20but%20as%20he%20settles%20into%20office%2C%20a%20further