0papers%20only.%20Where%20is%20it%20provided%20in%20the%20rules%20that%20you%20can%20put%20other%20marks%20in%20the%20ballot%20papers%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThen%20turning%20towards%20the%20solicitor%20general%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Solicitor%2C%20he%20has%20to%20be%20prosecuted.%20He%20was%20interfering%20with%20%5Bthe%5D%20election%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20the%20CJI%20said%20the%20bench%20itself%20will%20examine%20the%20ballots%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2020).%20It%20directed%20that%20the%20ballot%20papers%2C%20which%20have%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20registrar%20general%20of%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%2C%20be%20produced%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAll%20the%20necessary%20security%20arrangements%20must%20be%20made%20to%20ensure%20the%20safe%20transit%20of%20the%20judicial%20officer%20nominated%20by%20the%20registrar%20general%20as%20well%20as%20the%20safe%20custody%20of%20the%20ballot%20papers%2C%20the%20bench%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20bench%20also%20ordered%20the%20presiding%20officer%20to%20remain%20present%20during%20Tuesday%E2%80%99s%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ELater%2C%20it%20said%20it%20was%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20horse-trading%20that%20was%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20although%20the%20BJP%20mayor%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20amid%20rigging%20allegations%2C%20three%20AAP%20councillors%20joined%20the%20party%20in%20order%20to%20turn%20the%20tide%20in%20its%20favour%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20repoll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EReacting%20on%20the%20development%2C%20AAP%20supremo%20and%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20in%20Del