0you%20can%20take%20the%20premiership%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20said%20no%20to%20this.%20I%20said%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20a%20prime%20minister%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20become%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20it%20would%20be%20after%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20elect%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20taking%20any%20names%2C%20Bhutto-Zardari%20said%20the%20party%20had%20decided%20that%20it%20would%20move%20forward%20with%20%E2%80%9Cthose%20who%20have%20asked%20for%20its%20votes%E2%80%9D%20and%20would%20not%20seek%20any%20ministries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20his%20father%2C%20Zardari%2C%20would%20be%20the%20PPP%E2%80%99s%20nominee%20for%20the%20presidential%20slot%2C%20insisting%20that%20the%20former%20president%20would%20play%20his%20role%20to%20defuse%20political%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20control%20the%20fire%20spreading%20in%20the%20country%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20that%20Zardari%20will%20be%20our%20candidate%20for%20the%20presidential%20election.%20And%20when%20he%20takes%20up%20the%20post%2C%20he%20will%20put%20out%20this%20fire%2C%20and%20will%20save%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20provinces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20country%20needed%20a%20political%20party%20that%20talked%20about%20people%E2%80%99s%20problems%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20brewing%20economic%20and%20political%20crisis%20had%20divided%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20should%20happen%20is%20that%20politicians%20and%20all%20political%20parties%20should%20think%20about%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20their%20personal%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhutto-Zardari%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20foreign%20minister%20claimed%20that%20a%20PTI-backed%20candidate%20was%20made%20to%20win%20against%20a%20PPP%20leader.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20also%20had%20all%20the%20Form%2045s%20available%20with%20him%20and%20would%20approach%20the%20appropriate%20forum%20but%20%E2%80%9Cwouldn%E2%80%99t%20burn%20his%20own%20house%20down%20or%20divide%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20PPP%20had%20decided%20to%20collect%20the%20election%20complaints%20of%20party%20workers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20and%20raise%20them%20at%20appropriate%20forums.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20unsuccessful%2C%20we%20will%20come%20to%20you%20and%20protest%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EParties%20should%20%E2%80%98stay%20within%20system%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhutto-Zardari%20appealed%20to%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20%E2%80%9Cstay%20within%20the%20system%E2%80%9D%20and%20work%20for%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20betterment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20if%20we%20want%20to%20move%20ahead%20like%20this%20and%20spread%20this%20division%20of%20hate%20and%20politics%2C%20where%20someone%20tries%20to%20divide%20you%20along%20religious%20lines%2C%20then%20someone%20else%20would%20try%20to%20divide%20you%20along%20ethnic%20lines%20and%20someone%20else%20will%20try%20to%20divide%20through%20sectarianism%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDawn.com%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1815265%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20challenged%20Grand%20Democratic%20Alliance%20chief%20Pir%20Pagara%20and%20JUI-F%20chief%20Maulana%20Fazlur%20Rehman%20to%20bring%20all%20their%20Form%2045s%20to%20him%20and%20if%20proven%20wrong%2C%20he%20would%20contest%20polls%20against%20them%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20won%20two%20seats%2C%20out%20of%20which%20I%20will%20vacate%20one%20for%20by-elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20about%20you%20come%20and%20contest%20against%20us%20on%20that%20seat%3F%20Let%E2%80%99s%20see%20what%20your%20worth%20is.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C