%20towards%20life%20resonated%20with%20Suhasini%20and%20was%20instrumental%20in%20her%20falling%20in%20love%20with%20Atul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20lived%20alone%20in%20Mumbai%20for%2020%20years%20before%20meeting%20Atul%2C%20this%20is%20Suhasini%E2%80%99s%20first%20marriage.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20thought%20of%20getting%20married.%20You%20commit%20because%20you%20want%20to%2C%20not%20because%20society%20is%20pushing%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707915442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FAjrqPGWSJgE%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Remarriage%2C%20once%20taboo%2C%20is%20now%20embraced%2C%20exemplified%20by%20children%20advocating%20for%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20happiness.%20These%20Valentine%E2%80%99s%20Day%20tales%20of%20love%20underscore%20the%20timeless%20strength%20of%20love%20and%20the%20need%20for%20companionship%20at%20all%20ages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A48%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341793%2Fvalentines-day-love-stories-age-no-bar-senior-couples-remarriage-life-partners%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%203000%20Babies%20With%20Congenital%20Heart%20Diseases%20Have%20Been%20Saved%20By%20This%20Inspiring%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%20Khatoon%20(26)%20remembers%2022%20February%2C%202023%2C%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday%2C%20as%20she%20welcomed%20her%20first%20child%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306675%2Fanindita-chatterjee-travel-content-creator-new-mom-travelling-with-in