structure.%20Taking%20us%20on%20a%20virtual%20tour%20of%20the%20room%2C%20Shraddha%20says%20the%20decor%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20numbering%20the%20rooms%2C%20they%20are%20named%20after%20avatars%20of%20Lord%20Vishnu.%20The%20idea%20is%20for%20people%20to%20understand%20the%20history%20of%20Sawantwadi.%20When%20you%20enter%20a%20certain%20room%2C%20everything%20from%20the%20doorknob%20to%20the%20decor%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F90205%2F10-sustainable-homestays-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20of%20our%20artisans%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20has%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20symbols%20painted%20on%20them.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20inculcated%20the%20art%20in%20bits%20and%20pieces%20in%20the%20night%20lamps%2C%20the%20tea%20trays%20and%20everywhere%20we%20could%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20this%20is%20fascinating%2C%20Shraddha%20says%20you%20should%20hear%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20furniture.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20have%20been%20made%20by%20the%20Sawant%20Bhonsle%20family%20in%20their%20unit%20%E2%80%98Sawantwadi%20Lacquerwares%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20is%20also%20the%20place%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20revival%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20grandfather-in-law%20HH%20Rajesaheb%20Shivramraje%20Bhonsle%20visited%20the%20Victoria%20and%20Albert%20Museum%20in%20London%2C%20he%20noticed%20a%20label%20reading%20Sawantwadi%20Cards.%20He%20and%20his%20wife%20learnt%20the%20art%20from%20the%2080-year-old%20artist%20Pundalik%20Chitari%20who%20at%20that%20time%20would%20make%20only%20two%20sets%20of%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20year.%20They%20started%20Sawantwadi%20Lacquerwares%20in%201971%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338327%2Feco-vi